"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1931076-Andy-Murray-retires-Olympics-2024-tennis-news\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Andy Murrayhas bid farewell to tennis at the age of 37 after bowing out of theParis 2024 Olympicsin the men's doubles tournament.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The legendary Scot, a three-time Grand Slam winner and the most successful male British player of the Open era, had vowed to play one final tournament before retiring from the game.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But after an extraordinary run to the quarter-finals - which included comebacks against Kei Nishikori and Taro Daniels and Belgian pair Jorgan Vliegen and Sander Gille - he and his partnerDan Evans were beaten 6-2, 6-4 by Taylor Fritz and Tommy Paulfrom Team USA.\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 404, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kei Nishikori\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\"}, {\"begin\": 422, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro\", \"score\": 0.9999999999199645, \"rank\": 7.54211290689794e-11, \"text\": \"Taro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro\"}, {\"begin\": 439, \"end\": 446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9984761648808969, \"rank\": 0.0012834820125267508, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taylor Fritz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Fritz\"}, {\"begin\": 570, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9721397904080386, \"rank\": 0.028470616075167588, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite managing to fight back to 5-4 in the second set from a double break down, Murray and Evans were second best on the night at Roland Garros to bring the curtain down on Murray's phenomenal 18-year career.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.597977658877962e-52, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999138993600808, \"rank\": 8.610805382777936e-05, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 713, \"end\": 726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0217602890797793e-13, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 756, \"end\": 762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\