ce/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.998890896463244, \"rank\": 0.0011103318379111313, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray then struggled to hold back the tears himself as he headed towards the tunnel, before signing autographs for the fans.\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1353, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.597977658877962e-52, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former world No.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 won two gold medals in his career, beatingRoger Federerat the 2012 Olympics in London before defending his title in Rio de Janeiro in 2016.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1565, \"end\": 1578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999919596121, \"rank\": 8.04046326348405e-09, \"text\": \"2012 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennis_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1582, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9982512